viour of these amplitudes and we will determine if there is unitarity violation. For this it was also used the helicity base formalism.", "Data de Publicação": "2018-05-04", "url": "http://www.teses.usp.br/teses/disponiveis/43/43134/tde-03052018-135121/pt-br.php"}
